name: UNCEASING VIXEN 01:10
description: A nude female study from the photographic series titled Unceasing Vixens.  This image was created with a DSLR camera but was manipulated to look like it was taken with film. Simulated film grain and a light leak have been added to the image to give it a film look. A vixen is a fox and by definition is a spirited or fierce woman, specifically one seen as sexually attractive.
